thread.title: Scott

author: Scott
title: Scott
text: I am an ex-tradie with over 20 years experience manufacturing both commercial and domestic stainless steel kitchens. And the Swedia Cubex s/s tap that I ordered from Renevator Store was everything thing that I hoped it would be. And at half the price of the big name brands. They also had the customer service to match their top quality product. I have no problem recommending this great Aussie company.
